<h2>The $DKING Advantage in This Accumulation Zone</h2>

<p><strong>$DKING (DogeKing)</strong> demonstrated extreme relative strength during the June 2 selloff ” losing only -1.44% while BTC dropped -5.74% and most meme coins lost 7-10%. This outperformance is not random. It reflects:</p>

<ol>
<li><strong>Mature holder base:</strong> $DKING holders are not panic sellers. The community has been through multiple cycles and understands the accumulation game.</li>
<li><strong>Growing content ecosystem:</strong> With over 300 articles on dogeking.us, $DKING has one of the largest educational content libraries of any Solana meme coin ” a structural advantage that builds holder conviction.</li>
<li><strong>Low correlation to BTC during selloffs:</strong> $DKING's -1.44% vs BTC's -5.74% on a high-volume red day suggests decoupling from BTC downside while maintaining upside exposure.</li>
</ol>

<p>When the rotation comes ” and the data suggests it's coming within 24-72 hours ” assets that held strongest during the selloff are historically the ones that lead the recovery.</p>

<h2>Three-Phase Meme Coin Accumulation Strategy</h2>

<div class="accum-card">
