<div class="step"><span class="step-num">1</span> <strong>Set limit orders</strong> ” Place buy orders at current support levels for $DKING, BONK, and DOGE. Don't try to catch the exact bottom. Set orders at -5% below current price for meme coin leaders.</div>
<div class="step"><span class="step-num">2</span> <strong>Build a stablecoin war chest</strong> ” Keep 40-50% of your trading capital in USDC/USDT. The rotation will create opportunities that require dry powder.</div>
<div class="step"><span class="step-num">3</span> <strong>Monitor BTC.D hourly</strong> ” The trigger for Phase 2 is BTC.D dropping below 55.5% while BTC stays above $66K.</div>
</div>

<div class="accum-card">
