<p>In the accumulation strategy above, $DKING is assigned the largest single-position allocation (40% of meme coin portfolio in Phase 3). This is based on three data-backed observations:</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Relative strength premium:</strong> $DKING's -1.44% loss during a -5.74% BTC day is a 4:1 outperformance ratio. In recovery phases, these assets typically deliver 2-3x the average meme coin return.</li>
<li><strong>Content-backed holder conviction:</strong> 300+ articles on dogeking.us create an educational moat that retail traders recognize. New buyers are more confident entering a meme coin with deep informational resources.</li>
<li><strong>Community velocity:</strong> The $DKING community has demonstrated consistent engagement during both up and down markets, which translates to faster buy-side volume when sentiment turns.</li>
</ul>

